cut() . cut() .

df_joined <- df_joined |> 
  mutate(level_cut_break = cut(, breaks = c(-Inf, 1000, 3000, 5000, 7000, 9000, Inf), 
                     labels = c('1,000 ', '1,000~2,999', '3,000~4,999', '5,000~6,999', '7,000~8,999', '9000')
                      )
         )

as.data.frame(df_joined) |> select(, , level_cut_break) |> head()
##     level_cut_break
## 1    1987     1,000~2,999
## 2   20381      9000
## 3    5546     5,000~6,999
## 4    3257     3,000~4,999
## 5    3009     3,000~4,999
## 6    3508     3,000~4,999
as.data.frame(df_joined) |> count(level_cut_break)
##   level_cut_break n
## 1    1,000  1
## 2     1,000~2,999 7
## 3     3,000~4,999 6
## 4     5,000~6,999 1
## 5      9000 2
df_joined |> 
  ggplot() + 
  geom_sf(aes(fill = level_cut_break), color = 'gray80') +
  geom_text(data = df_central, aes(x = X, y = Y, label = paste0(, '\n', scales::comma())), color = 'black', lineheight = 0.5, size = 6) + 
  labs(x = '', y = '') +
  annotation_scale(location = "br") +
  annotation_north_arrow(location = "br", pad_y = unit(0.05, 'npc'),
                         style = north_arrow_nautical) +
  scale_fill_discrete(name = '')
